{"type":"session_message","session_id":"ses_28953d1b4ffefBDzvj1zJ5vKVY","role":"assistant","message_id":"msg_d76b43b1a00120FNBoSr1nHqAQ","parts":[{"id":"prt_d76b44187002tqiUff53Fzax6g","messageID":"msg_d76b43b1a00120FNBoSr1nHqAQ","sessionID":"ses_28953d1b4ffefBDzvj1zJ5vKVY","type":"text","text":"## 仓库配置完成报告\n\n### 环境配置\n\n**已安装的依赖：**\n| 包 | 版本 |\n|---|---|\n| Python | 3.11.2 |\n| torch | 2.5.1+cpu |\n| torchvision | 0.20.1+cpu |\n| numpy | 2.4.4 |\n| scikit-learn | 1.8.0 |\n| tqdm | 4.67.3 |\n| pytorch-metric-learning | 2.9.0 (editable) |\n\n### 验证测试结果\n\n**运行成功的测试：**\n- `tests.losses.test_angular_loss` - 3/3 ✓\n- `tests.losses.test_triplet_margin_loss` - 4/4 ✓\n- `tests.losses.test_contrastive_loss` - 3/3 ✓\n- `tests.losses.test_circle_loss` - 3/3 ✓\n- `tests.losses.test_arcface_loss` - 1/1 ✓\n- `tests.losses.test_cosface_loss` - 1/1 ✓\n- `tests.losses.test_cross_batch_memory` - 9/9 ✓\n- `tests.losses.test_nca_loss` - 2/2 ✓\n- `tests.losses.test_margin_loss` - 4/4 ✓\n- `tests.losses.test_lifted_structure_loss` - 4/4 ✓\n- `tests.losses.test_npairs_loss` - 3/3 ✓\n- `tests.miners.test_multi_similarity_miner` - 2/2 ✓\n- `tests.miners.test_triplet_margin_miner` - 2/2 ✓\n- `tests.miners.test_batch_hard_miner` - 5/5 ✓\n- `tests.miners.test_distance_weighted_miner` - 3/3 ✓\n- `tests.distances.test_batched_distance` - 2/2 ✓\n- `tests.samplers.test_hierarchical_sampler` - 1/1 ✓\n- `tests.samplers.test_m_per_class_sampler` - 2/2 ✓\n- `tests.reducers.test_mean_reducer` - 1/1 ✓\n- `tests.regularizers.*` - 2/2 ✓\n- `tests.utils.test_loss_tracker` - 1/1 ✓\n\n**失败的测试（2 个）：**\n1. `tests.losses.test_large_margin_softmax_loss.test_large_margin_softmax_and_sphereface_loss` - 浮点数精度差异\n2. `tests.losses.test_ntxent_loss.test_ntxent_loss_with_ref` - 浮点数精度差异\n\n失败原因：这两个测试使用严格的容差 (`rtol=1e-5`) 比较浮点数结果，CPU 版本的 PyTorch 与 GPU 版本在浮点数计算上存在细微差异。\n\n**代码质量检查：**\n- `flake8 src` - 0 个问题 ✓\n\n**端到端测试：**\n- 基本功能测试 ✓\n- 端到端训练模拟 ✓\n\n### 关键改动\n1. 安装 pip (`apt-get install python3-pip`)\n2. 安装依赖：`numpy`, `scikit-learn`, `tqdm`, `torch` (CPU 版本), `torchvision` (CPU 版本)\n3. 以 editable 模式安装仓库：`pip install -e /workspace`\n\n### 结论\n✅ **仓库配置成功**。pytorch-metric-learning v2.9.0 已成功安装并可正常运行。核心功能（losses、miners、distances、reducers、regularizers、samplers）均通过测试。2 个测试失败是由于 CPU 版本 PyTorch 的浮点数精度差异，不影响实际使用。","time":{"start":1775813032395,"end":1775813032395}}]}
